cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.FL, cs.SE, cs.SC 

The paper deals with termination analysis of term rewriting, which is a topic in the area of logic and computation (cs.LO). The paper also introduces a higher-order dependency pair framework, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and formal languages (cs.FL). The implementation of the framework in the WANDA tool suggests a software engineering (cs.SE) aspect. Finally, the paper discusses the advantages and disadvantages of two existing approaches, which could be considered as a form of scientific computing (cs.SC).
